headline: Dell Taps AI India Blueprint And McLaren To Support Growth Narrative
summary: Dell Technologies (NYSE:DELL) has introduced an "AI India Blueprint" focused on supporting national AI infrastructure and secure, large scale deployments. The company has also extended its partnership with McLaren Racing, expanding the use of Dell AI and high performance computing across racing operations. These moves highlight Dell's push into both sovereign AI capabilities in India and data intensive, real time AI use cases in elite motorsport. Dell Technologies, trading at $122.27, sits...
